      "dateCreated": "2026-03-21",
      "description": "Reproduces the single-nucleus multiome (joint snRNA-seq + scATAC-seq) analysis from 'Epithelial WNT secretion drives niche escape of developing gastric cancer'. Processes 10x Genomics snMultiome data for Wild-type (RZ) and KRAS-mutant (RZK) mouse gastric samples through QC, MACS2 peak calling, SCTransform normalization, SCT-based integration, clustering, cell-type annotation, differential expression (MAST), differential accessibility, and JASPAR2020 motif enrichment. Uses Seurat v5 with v4 compatibility mode for stable reproducibility. Validated with real data producing all figures (3A-3I, S3B-S3C).",
